title: Aynbath Artbook: Astral monument. Black Edition
description: First edition of the first official Artbook of Aynbath. Finally a compendium consisting of characters, places, spells and tales of the first years of Aynbath. Accompanied by intriguing texts and stories this is a diverse collection of ideas and artwork in many styles. It also contains exclusive revamps of a few beloved older artworks and also paintings that will only be featured in this book.Bilingual: German - English
author: Aerozopher
